2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses machine learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks, for the automatic detection and quantification of knee osteoarthritis severity. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses artificial intelligence techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks, for the automatic detection and quantification of knee osteoarthritis severity. 
4. cs.MS (Medical Imaging) - The paper deals with medical imaging, specifically X-ray images of knee joints, and proposes a new approach for automatically detecting knee joints and quantifying knee osteoarthritis severity. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with multimedia content, specifically X-ray images, and proposes a new approach for automatically detecting knee joints and quantifying knee osteoarthritis severity.
